<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.3.8">
<l>kēṭṭaṟi yātaṉa kēṭkiṉṟēṉ kēcavā kōvala rinti raṟku</l>
<l>kāṭṭiya cōṟuṅ kaṟiyun tayiruṅ kalantuṭa ṉuṇṭāy pōlu</l>
<l>mūṭṭa mutalilē ṉuṉtaṉṉaik koṇṭoru pōtumeṉak karitu</l>
<l>vāṭṭa milāppukaḻ vācutē vāvuṉṉai yañcuva ṉiṉṟu toṭṭum</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kesava, I am hearing unfathomable things!</l>
<l>It seems that, having mixed up the rice, curry, and curd</l>
<l rend="indent">that the herders offered to Indra,</l>
<l>You ate [them all up] at once!</l>
<l>I do not have the money to feed [you],</l>
<l rend="indent">it is difficult for me [to] provide for you at this time.</l>
<l>Vāsudeva of unfading glory! Now I am beginning to fear you.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
